<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>🎆 完璧！スレッド作成完了 🎆</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <style>
    body, html {
      margin: 0; padding: 0; height: 100%;
      background: #0c0c1a;
      font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      color: #fff;
    }
    .card {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 20px;
      max-width: 360px;
      text-align: center;
      box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
      color: #222;
    }
    h1 {
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      color: #0077ff;
    }
    p {
      font-size: 1rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
    }
    a.btn {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      background: #0077ff;
      color: #fff;
      border-radius: 30px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 1rem;
      transition: background 0.3s;
    }
    a.btn:hover {
      background: #005fcc;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="card">
    <h1>スレッドを<br>作成しました</h1>
    <p>🎉 あなたのスレッドが投稿されました！</p>
    <a class="btn" href="/threads/<%= threadId %>">作成したスレッドを見る →</a>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
